    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011890/extras/4a33e66fe63391876c7e1ef879a2de78.poster.avif?t=1761240958\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011890/extras/4a33e66fe63391876c7e1ef879a2de78.webm?t=1761240958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011890/extras/4a33e66fe63391876c7e1ef879a2de78.mp4?t=1761240958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Prank targets while evading the dastardly Fun Police, then try to escape without getting caught! Plan your approach to each level: will you unleash complete mayhem or sneak through undetected? The choice is yours! Explore intriguing locales, meet wacky characters, and utilize your arsenal of clown props to bring joy back to the world!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >TONS OF EQUIPMENT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > This game features a large selection<strong> </strong>of <strong>unique and wacky</strong> tools for you to use with multiple goofy interactions waiting to be discovered!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011890/extras/c7bf15e7bac9c62e5d679c6467f6b01a.poster.avif?t=1761240958\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011890/extras/c7bf15e7bac9c62e5d679c6467f6b01a.webm?t=1761240958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011890/extras/c7bf15e7bac9c62e5d679c6467f6b01a.mp4?t=1761240958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >REACTIVE AND DYNAMIC WORLD</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > NPC's have a set schedule and <strong>react to the things you do </strong>which also affects how they interact with each other. If they get pranked or see you playing pranks they will get upset and can take out that frustration on others causing a domino effect of complete pandemonium!   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011890/extras/0dd5f4c9ee159cc86f6f4da2aaa58dff.poster.avif?t=1761240958\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011890/extras/0dd5f4c9ee159cc86f6f4da2aaa58dff.webm?t=1761240958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011890/extras/0dd5f4c9ee159cc86f6f4da2aaa58dff.mp4?t=1761240958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >OPTIONS AND REPLAYABILITY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > There's no wrong way to play the game, <strong>complete missions any way you want</strong>. Plan your approach and discover alternate routes, then try missions again using a different strategy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011890/extras/8e28870529ea177bc6be17cfcacaba14.poster.avif?t=1761240958\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011890/extras/8e28870529ea177bc6be17cfcacaba14.webm?t=1761240958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011890/extras/8e28870529ea177bc6be17cfcacaba14.mp4?t=1761240958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXPLORATION AND SECRETS</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level is densely packed with interesting things to see and <strong>hidden secrets to find</strong>. You might uncover a hidden piece of equipment, or maybe discover a secret way to play a prank. Keep your eyes (and bananas) peeled!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011890/extras/1a47b64eaa3b51f2fcfb40a854a9f715.poster.avif?t=1761240958\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011890/extras/1a47b64eaa3b51f2fcfb40a854a9f715.webm?t=1761240958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011890/extras/1a47b64eaa3b51f2fcfb40a854a9f715.mp4?t=1761240958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><u><i><strong>WISHLIST NOW AND STAY TUNED FOR UPDATES!</strong></i></u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011890/extras/51404568e19322e667ed1503282767ad.poster.avif?t=1761240958\" width=608 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011890/extras/51404568e19322e667ed1503282767ad.webm?t=1761240958\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3011890/extras/51404568e19322e667ed1503282767ad.mp4?t=1761240958\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p>",
